# 지도시각화

## #01. 필요한 모듈 참조

> pip install --upgrade folium


```python
import folium
```

## #02. 지도 표현하기

1) 지도 객체 생성


```python
# zoom_start : 배율 1~22
map_osm = folium.Map(location =[43.7696674,-79.4159717], zoom_start=17)
map_osm
```




<div style="width:100%;"><div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:0;padding-bottom:60%;"><iframe src="data:text/html;charset=utf-8;base64," style="position:absolute;width:100%;height:100%;left:0;top:0;border:none !important;" allowfullscreen webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen></iframe></div></div>



2) 지도객체에 마커 추가

일반마커


```python
marker1 = folium.Marker([43.7696674,-79.4159717], popup='Gibson', icon=folium.Icon(color='red', icon='info-sign'))
marker1.add_to(map_osm)
map_osm
```




<div style="width:100%;"><div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:0;padding-bottom:60%;"><iframe src="data:text/html;charset=utf-8;base64," style="position:absolute;width:100%;height:100%;left:0;top:0;border:none !important;" allowfullscreen webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen></iframe></div></div>



구름아이콘


```python
marker2 = folium.Marker([43.7696674,-79.4159717], popup='Gibson', icon=folium.Icon(color='blue', icon='cloud'))
marker2.add_to(map_osm)
map_osm
```




<div style="width:100%;"><div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:0;padding-bottom:60%;"><iframe src="data:text/html;charset=utf-8;base64," style="position:absolute;width:100%;height:100%;left:0;top:0;border:none !important;" allowfullscreen webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen></iframe></div></div>



원형마커(범위지정)


```python
marker3 = folium.CircleMarker([43.7696674,-79.4159717], radius = 300, color ='#3186cc', fill_color='#3186cc', popup='Gibson')
marker3.add_to(map_osm)
map_osm
```
